<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Spawn time has been reduced on Babbinsbort a hell of a lot. i was in WC, some paladin ahad killed the necro 5 minutes ago and was asking what the icon was for. I told him that i needed it, so he said he would help me get it.  We went back into befallen, he checked the spawn, and low and behold,there was babbinsbort.  He brought it up to first floor, killed it, and let me loot.  So basically the spawn time was about 10-15 mins.  He was a low 30s paladin and only lost a few bubbles of health to the necro.  Hope this helped all of you questing clerics out there.  Now all i gotta do is get the plat bar and the thing at the bottom of the everfrost river...<BR>
