<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I've run this quest 3 times in the past month. The trick is just stopping by Befallen on your run through WC to see if Babbin is home. I have soloed him 4 times...and yes he killed me once at 30 (those damn necro DOTs hurt).  Once you get the Icon just run to Everfrost for the ingot and your basically done.  Of course there is always faction and an echanted plat bar.<BR>
<BR>
Good luck. <BR>
