<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok a couple things...<BR>
The icon is under the river in everfrost very close to the loc 3000 -5200. it looks like a bag until you pick it up. Babbinsport is a very tough necro. When i attacked him his first DOT he hit me with took away about 200hp. He has about 550hp and his pet has slighlty more. He dropped the ingot and a dagger. You also need a galvanized plat bar, to get this give Genni an enchanted plat bar. She is up on the 3rd floor of the temple of Sol ro. Hope this helps someone</font></td></tr></table>
