<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: legerian</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-09-30 20:04:10</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>here is a little secret for those of u who dont want to bother finding someone to cast DMF or enduring breath on u.  While swimming under the ice, you can actully go to the side, where the ice touches the ground, and get a new breath. Try it a few times to get the hang of it...takes a few times to get.  Dont swim until you are almost out of breath, and then try it, you will most likely die.  Another thing that is cool, is that once you have picked it up...you can do the same trick, go to the edge of the ice and get a breath, but if you now turn away from the edge and swim upwards, you will pop out of the river, right through the ice.  Hopefully the wont nerf this cause its not that big of a deal...im just really bored, so im telling everyone.</font></td></tr></table>
