<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Ellrond</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-03 16:58:49</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is my second time doing the quest and I couldn't find the ingot. I went to the loc again (2984, -5717) a day later and found it, the ingot sits on the edge of a triangular shaped slab. After doing some tests I found the ingot spawns between 10 and 18 hours, so if it isn't there you might have a long wait. If you need galvanized plat talk to the quest giver for this item, I think she tells you to give an enchanted bar of platinum to Genni, and Genni will give you a galvanized bar. Babbinsport has less then 600hps (dead in one nuke).<BR>
<BR>
Ellrond -Maelstorm's Furry<BR>
45 Wizard</font></td></tr></table>
